_:N6f209079a9c04654bd683c4177d676d9 <http://schema.org/description> "The Review Body on Doctors’ and Dentists’ Remuneration (DDRB) advises government on rates of pay for doctors and dentists. DDRB is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department of Health and Social Care ." .
